          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "The screens displaying news of the day hang just long enough for you to almost finish reading the summary. Then it changes, I was invested enough to read all bulletins waiting for the first one to come back up again so I could finish it. Clever design? Or am I a slow reader? ",
