            "content": " use of twenty minutes on an airplane. Doubly scrap that, I was right the first time; and I’ve got a photo to prove it. The zigzags are offset by 180 degrees (if my maths is right) basically the peak is in line with the tough of the zigzag above. Ok I feel like I’ve beat this pattern horse a bit too much, I’m starting to feel bad. Shit one more correction, the amplitude doesn’t decrease - that was just a trick of the eye as the wing curved. Ok done, promise 🤞",
